🏀 - How does this collection create new players?

A: New characters create new ways to play. 

Firstly, we wanted to reward holders who have stuck with us.

RKL gives them an opportunity to help onboard new players & provides them with more players to choose from in-game.👍

7/9 https://t.co/PQh2js8BGe

🦍 - What keeps Kongs higher in value & rarity than other NFTs who play in the games ecosystem?

A: Kongs will always be our genesis drop & therefore will receive the highest benefits.🔥

Kongs are the only collection that can play in Clubs & compete in the official RKL. 

6/9 https://t.co/rqpOR1QJyD

⚡- Can Rookies end up with higher boosts than Kongs?

A: We will soon share how boosts with non-Kong avatars will work. 

This is still being internally finalized, which is why we decided to mint Rookies without boosts.🏀

5/9 https://t.co/gBidOeA3aF

🎮 - Will Rookies be playable in-game?

A: Yes.

⚡ - Will Rookies have boosts?

A: Initially, Rookies will not have boosts, they will be unlocked later once they start playing games. 

Only when you see your rookie on the court will you know if you’ve got a future all-star!

4/9 https://t.co/tNzQKLGuVr

🔶 - Will rare furs be guaranteed rare fur mints?

A: They will not, all mints will be random.

❓- Are rarity traits done like Kongs (top 250) or completely random?

A: Traits will be distributed in the same respect as Kongs, meaning there will be 250 rare-looking Rookies.

3/9 https://t.co/3MHVUEv6Lm

A: The 11th of August

5/ We envision clubs going beyond the RKL by building their own brand identities, forming communities, and pushing their vision forward. 

There are no limits, we aim to give anyone an opportunity to launch a native web3 brand, and we see RKL as the bridge to make it happen.

4/ Next to gameplay, Clubs offer various possibilities...

◾️ Media Rights
◾️ Revenue Share
◾️ League Payouts
◾️ Custom Arenas
◾️ Ingame Branding
◾️ Individual Jerseys
◾️ Custom Tournaments
◾️ Integrated Merch Store

https://t.co/iybI5sSHUW

3/ As you see, Clubs are, next to Kongs, the deepest level of engagement you can have with the RKL. 

They are an opportunity to build a brand from scratch, form a team, and participate in the Ranked Leagues game-modes, where a total of 300 clubs will compete for fame and honor.

2/ We are aiming to have 3 levels of gameplay. 

🏀Ranked Leagues - for Clubs & Kongs, providing the best possible earning potential
🏀Ranked Play - for Kongs and other PFPs with Play&Earn
🏀Casual Play - for users who don't have a wallet(yet) and without Play&Earn https://t.co/2nnTlM5LQQ

1/ @RumbleKongs is the metaverse sports league, we are currently developing a web&mobile game, giving web3 avatars the chance to compete in 3v3 basketball matches. 

The players will be Kongs, or other PFP collections. We want to give everyone the opportunity to play and earn.

@_miketriumph_ Probably a week of heads up, around that time. For limitation we haven't decided yet but very likely for 1 or 2 only per wallet.
Of course this can be exploited, but we'd like to get a large bunch of clubs onboarded officially.

Additionally we will increase the club raffle number from 2 to 4, for the "OG Clubs" listed at the bottom of the article. 

Learn more about clubs here 👇
https://t.co/9QmfRO4moM
We hope that you welcome this change, as we want to keep clubs special, but at the same time level the playing field a bit to make them more affordable, through increased supply.

The first wave remains only open to existing Kong holders and we will share updated details about all the details soon.

Our current bottleneck remains web front-end but we should have this sorted out very soon to launch the first club wave.

Clubs are, next to Kongs, the center piece of what RKL is about. A community within a community, to come together and play and earn with.

We feel that increasing the first wave will offer more clubs the opportunity to become official, while making them more overall attainable.

PSA: The https://t.co/ZOyC3UojEB website lists a large number of unofficial RKL clubs.
With the first club wave happening soon, we've decided to increase the number of club auctions from 13, up to 50 clubs in the first wave.

🏀Just getting started!
A lot is coming including

- Brand new website
- Staking
- Clubs and more

Soon we will be announcing further partners joining the RKL with vast sports, entertainment, and gaming industry experience. 

We are just getting started! 🚀

🏀What's Next?
The Kong community will be heavily involved in game decisions over the coming months.

We will be sharing:
- Dev Diaries
- WIP visuals
- Teasers
- Community Voting

and a whole lot more..

🏀IP Rights
The RKL team maintains 100% ownership and has the final word on all development matters, together with Kong community.

We decided against the traditional centralized publisher route as this was critical for us.

This is #Web3 after-all.. TRUE ownership!🔥

🏀Work Has Begun!
Work on the Rumble Kong League game has already begun.

Current status is pre-production, focus is nailing down economics, core game loop, and the game's look & feel.🎨

The game will be 3D, initially Web-based with a mobile version following.

🏀About iLogos
iLogos is a full-cycle development and game production studio that has worked with publishers including Supercell, Ubisoft, EA, Disney, and many more.

Some stats:
- 14+ years experience
- 400+ game projects
- 1B+ game installs

ERC-20 TOKEN 💰

We will release a token as part of our roadmap, fueling the game economy.
Used to participate in leagues, get consumables, customize your Kong, or give Clubs additional features.

More features and use-cases will be added along the way. 💰

ACADEMIES / STAKING 📈

🔸User have the possibility to stake their Kong prior to the game launch to improve their boost
🔸Feature released for early adopters prior actual game launch
🔸Kongs in Academies (staked) will be removed from the total supply for the duration of training.

GAMEPLAY 🎮

🔸Initially hand-off, algorithmic gameplay to launch the first version. User input will be minimal and more tactical based
🔸Watch your Kong play, cheer for him scoring, support your team mates, find the right strategy.
🔸 Arcade style on wishlist https://t.co/VhqicQ4V1d

LEAGUES & TOURNAMENTS 🏆

🔸Everyone can play pick up matches, but only clubs can play competitively 
🔸Clubs will assemble the best of the best, and give Kongs of all skill-levels a chance to win.
🔸Even low-boost Kongs can win their respective leagues 🔥 https://t.co/I0b4QE4NM1

CLUBS 🏀

🔸Unreleased standalone #NFT that focuses on management over games
🔸Highly customisable with logos, colours, lineups, tactics, sponsors,...
🔸Clubs are needed to play competitively in leagues and tournaments
🔸Release date tbd

Who will be the #1 Club?

❤️All NFTs welcome

We want to build an inclusive ecosystem where every avatar is welcome.
Users can "import" their avatar into the Rumble Kong League.
Imagine a basketball game of Kongs against apes, whales, skeletons, raptors, or anything else really!

What are Kongs? 🦍

🔸10,000 unique Avatar #NFTs
🔸Each Kong will be a player in our upcoming 3v3 basketball #PlayToEarn game
🔸Each Kong looks unique with Boosts that determine his initial game perf. 
🔸Future features include levels, naming, and stamina
🔸They are damn sexy https://t.co/Qdlche49D3
